<% title "About this Website" %>
 <h2>Overview</h2>
<p>BHRobotics.com is the website for the FRC team MorTorq (number 1515) based in Beverly Hills, California. It serves as a portal for information about our team and the FIRST Robotics program. It contains information on the team itself and resources on how build a FIRST site and the history of the program.</p>
