  <h2>Student Designed, Student Built</h2>
<p>This website was designed by student members of the team. We wrote all of the content and all of the code. We utilize the modern web framework Ruby on Rails, ensuring that our site is completely flexible to our needs. This setup also allows us to learn and teach modern programming standards to our members. Content management systems like Wordpress, nice as they are, would not allow us to do this. The site design is also completely original using sprites we made.</p>
