  <h2>Supporting Emerging Web Standards</h2> 
<p>BHRobotics.com fully complies with modern web technologies such as HTML5, CSS3, Ruby on Rails, Postgre SQL, and Git. This keeps our site looking sharp and and working smoothly. For this reason, we recommend upgrading your web browser to the latest version, but it will work fine even if you don't :). </p>
<%= image_tag 'HTML5_Logo_512.png', :alt => 'HTML5 Logo' %>

  <h2>Helping Others</h2>
<p>One of FIRST's most important themes is the Spirit of Coopertition. It is every team's duty to help each other. This is why BHRobotics.com contains a "Create Your Own First Site" page to help other teams with their own site. Users will be able to learn the techniques necessary to build their own advanced website for their FRC Team. We also contain a Build and Safety Manual for build members.</p>
